e387e708f89a9104cc7a64","tid":1472380,"uid":227918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rYZRyGM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrYZRyGM.png&h=5994379f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係之前既時候 cr既客服團隊曾經告知小弟cr既玩家係享有言論自由<br />\n<br />\n所以小弟今日屎忽痕做左個壓力測試 睇下會唔會被改名做皇室精英<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TWVtAVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTWVtAVS.png&h=5459b7b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我就拎左正身去比五百石改左個名<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mxBwyH7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmxBwyH7.png&h=18acd76b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果四個鐘之後就變左做<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jf14THQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjf14THQ.png&h=83d9da77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（跌左200分係因為連輸左好多場）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後雖然明知好似屌政府咁一樣冇用但都單方面係客服度屌左好耐<br />\n<br />\n最嬲係改還改 你改我做香港加油我都可以扮冇野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsorry for1999<br />\n個ac平時剩係拎黎睇成人台同睇而加既環境<br />\n第一次開post唔知有冇打錯格式<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位巴絲一齊壓力測試<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n#錫春袋都唔割<br />\n#香港加油"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:25:44.000Z","msg":"咁佢有冇俾返500石你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:40:29.000Z","msg":"緊係冇啦 點會比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:57:09.000Z","msg":"做咩唔投訴佢<br />\n<br />\n你itune俾嘅<br />\n<br />\n用依個理由全退你itune俾嘅錢都得<br />\n<br />\n以前有第二隻game買野冇俾我<br />\n<br />\n我上佢官網同app store投訴<br />\n<br />\n隻game俾返D野我<br />\n<br />\nApp store退返錢俾我<br />\n<br />\n你買咗野唔俾你改名緊係可以追返佢<br />\n<br />\n不過佢封你AC就可以去app store 申請全退"},{"pid":"0dd5452c5f829aa7fccd9863620706f2af7f5308","tid":1472380,"uid":227918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c738d4be963cafcd9ec8a1fbb50e36db79a5473","tid":1472380,"uid":14171,"like":2,"dislike":0